  m_text: 'In this level, you will connect important learning theories with the theorists
    who developed them.Read each theory carefully and Identify the theorist associated
    with that theory.


    Each question allows only one attempt.

    If your answer
    is correct, the answer button will glow green and you will receive +10 points.

    If
    your answer is wrong, the answer button will turn red and you will not receive
    points.

    You cannot change your answer after selection.


    Click           
    to start the game.


    Good Luck!'
